<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1"&gt;1 Ekakanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1/1.1"&gt;1.1 Paṭhamavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;1.1.1 Lobhasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Ekakanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Paṭhamavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Lobhasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_2"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;1.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_3"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;“Ekadhammaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāya. Katamaṃ ekadhammaṃ? Lobhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekadhammaṃ pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāyā”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_4"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;4&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Yena lobhena luddhāse,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Taṃ lobhaṃ sammadaññāya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pajahanti vipassino;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Pahāya na punāyanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;imaṃ lokaṃ kudācanan”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_5"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_6"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;Paṭhamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="266882" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 1.1 Paṭhamavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="266882" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="268377" title="Go to next page"&gt;1.1.2 Dosasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
